<Defs>
	<!-- Bear - Boomalope -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase">
		<defName>GR_Bearalope</defName>
		<label>bearalope</label>
		<description>An unusual concoction of traits that was favoured by a particular client who was obsessed on making things explode. Earned the nickname Boom-Boom as they would often make requests along the lines of “two more booms, wasn’t paying attention”.\n\nAn ursine hybrid with recessive boomalope genes. Lacking intelligence compared to a bear while also missing out on some strength and confidence in hunting. However, they can be commanded to detonate a limited amount of fuel sacks for increased combat versatility in exchange for hurting themselves intentionally.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Gameplay effect:&lt;/color&gt; All primary bear hybrids have stun attacks. The "Detonate chemfuel" ability can be used to cause a powerful "Bomb" damage type explosion surrounding the hybrid. Bear in mind (pun intended) that this will damage the hybrid too!</description>
		<statBases>
			<MoveSpeed>4.0</MoveSpeed>
			<ComfyTemperatureMin>-30</ComfyTemperatureMin>
			<MarketValue>550</MarketValue>
			<LeatherAmount>25</LeatherAmount>
			<FilthRate>4</FilthRate>
		</statBases>
		<tools>
			<li>
				<label>left claw</label>
				<capacities>
					<li>Scratch</li>
				</capacities>
				<power>13</power>
				<cooldownTime>2.0</cooldownTime>
				<linkedBodyPartsGroup>FrontLeftPaw</linkedBodyPartsGroup>
				<surpriseAttack>
					<extraMeleeDamages>
						<li>
							<def>Stun</def>
							<amount>18</amount>
						</li>
					</extraMeleeDamages>
				</surpriseAttack>
			</li>
			<li>
				<label>right claw</label>
				<capacities>
					<li>Scratch</li>
				</capacities>
				<power>13</power>
				<cooldownTime>2.0</cooldownTime>
				<linkedBodyPartsGroup>FrontRightPaw</linkedBodyPartsGroup>
				<surpriseAttack>
					<extraMeleeDamages>
						<li>
							<def>Stun</def>
